===Etymology 1===
[[Image:Biber-drawing.jpg|thumb|Beavers]]
From {{inh|en|enm|bever}}, from {{inh|en|ang|beofor||beaver}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*bebruz||beaver}} (compare {{cog|fy|bever}}, {{cog|nl|bever}}, {{cog|fr|bièvre}}, {{cog|de|Biber}}, dialectal {{cog|sv|bjur}}), from {{inh|en|ine-pro|*bʰébʰrus||beaver}} (compare {{cog|cy|befer}}, {{cog|la|fiber}}, {{cog|lt|bẽbras}}, {{cog|ru|бобр}}, {{cog|ae|𐬠𐬀𐬎𐬎𐬭𐬀}}, {{m|ae|𐬠𐬀𐬎𐬎𐬭𐬌}}, {{cog|sa|बभ्रु|tr=bábhru|t=mongoose; ichneumon}}), from {{der|en|ine-pro|*bʰerH-||brown}}. Related to {{m|en|brown}} and {{m|en|bear}}.

